responsible for today's abortive coup plot because of their
alleged failure to open talks.
</P>
<P>
He called on the Zambians to protect their peaceful country at
all cost, saying that "if they destroy it now through violence
means, it will be difficult to regain what has been lost and the
ordinary citizens will suffer greatly."
</P>
<P>
Some of the causes to the current political crisis in the
country are poverty, diseases and hunger, he said,and for this
reason, the government should put measures in place to address
them seriously and immediately. 
