Museveni returned home today after attending the 1997
Commonwealth heads of state summit in Edinburgh, Scotland, which
ended its deliberations Monday.
</P>
<P>
During the summit, Commonwealth leaders recommended themselves
to democracy, good governance, sustainable development and
respect for human rights.
</P>
<P>
In the communique issued at the conclusion of the meeting, the
