proved guilty through the courts of law.
</P>
<P>
"Under the democratic system, patience must prevail and so we
will wait for the courts of law to prove the culprits guilty
before we can act," he said.
</P>
<P>
On the occasion, students union chairman Isaac Lungu said
military coups are retrogressive to the country's development.
</P>
<P>
He called on the government to ensure that there is meaningful
dialogue with the opposition to resolve their differences.
