<TEXT>
<P>
TUNIS, October 29 (Xinhua) -- South African President Nelson
Mandela arrived this morning in the Libyan town of Zuwara, 120
kilometers west of Tripoli, for a second meeting with Libyan
leader Muammar Gaddafi in a week.
</P>
<P>
Gaddafi welcomed Mandela on his arrival, the Jamahiriya News
Agency of Libya said.
</P>
<P>
