<HEADLINE> Gold Price in Hong Kong Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, October 29 (Xinhua) -- The gold price in Hong Kong
rose 17 HK dollars today to close at 2,897 HK dollars a
tael, according to Po Sang Bank, one of the major gold dealers in
Hong Kong.
</P>
<P>
