At the same time, airport facilities remain "heavily
under-utilized" during the day, he said.
</P>
<P>
Stating that such under-utilization of expensive facilities can
not be afforded, Ibrahim called for rescheduling of flights so
that utilization is spread evenly.
</P>
<P>
This would also provide greater comfort to passengers, the
minister added. 
