<HEADLINE> Pure Gold Cards Issued to Mark Fifth China Arts Festival </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CHENGDU, October 29 (Xinhua) -- Two sets of souvenir cards made
of pure gold were issued across China to commemorate the ongoing
Fifth China Arts Festival.
</P>
<P>
The Organizing Committee of the Fifth China Arts Festival
issued 3,000 sets of gold cards -- one of 10 cards each and the
other of three cards -- and destroyed the moulds.
</P>
<P>
