scenic spots of Sichuan Province. The reverse side of the cards is
etched with pictures of cultural relics unearthed in Sanxingdui
ruins in the city of Guanghan, about 40 kilometers north of
Chengdu, capital of Sichuan Province. The discovery is considered
one of China's most important archaeological discoveries this
century.
</P>
<P>
The ongoing arts festival is the last art gathering of the
century and the the biggest ever. The Hong Kong Special
Administrative Region (SAR) sent a delegation to the festival for
the first time.
</P>
<P>
The fifth China Art Festival, sponsored by the Ministry of
Culture, began Oct. 25 and is scheduled to close Nov. 5 in
Chengdu. 
