<P>
The Aviation Department has approved Thai Air Cargo Co. to fly
from Bangkok to Maynamr, China, Korea, Singapore and China's Hong
Kong starting in January, press reports said.
</P>
<P>
Thai Air Cargo is now preparing to lease aircraft, develop
flight schedules and train staff.
</P>
<P>
A source at the department was quoted as saying that Thai Air
Cargo would have a tough job competing with 76 airlines flying
into and out of Bangkok.  
</P>
</TEXT>
