Xiaolangdi water control project, Chinese Vice-minister of Water
Resources Zhang Jiyao told reporters Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
The successful damming of the Yellow River that morning is a
key achievement in the project, and was the result of the hard
work of all Chinese and foreign workers, Zhang said.
(China-Xiaolangdi-Cooperation)
