Henan province.
</P>
<P>
The dam is the 12th on the river and marks the beginning of the
construction of the Xiaolangdi Multi-Purpose Water Control
Project. Its main purpose is to prevent the perennial flooding,
which has been referred to as the "sorrow of the Chinese nation".
</P>
