Ahmed Salama, acting editor-in-chief and first editor of Egypt's
"Al-Ahram" newspaper, in Beijing, where Premier Li explained the
main tasks of political restructuring.
</P>
<P>
-- Chinese Premier Li Peng, speaking yesterday at a ceremony to
mark the successful damming of the Yellow River at Xiaolangdi,
called the dam work a gratifying sign of progress made in taming
the river.
